Identity Theft Protection – company paid

About the job
Build intelligent traffic engineering platform / SDN controllers for network traffic management, monitoring, targeting and traffic data analysis.
Design innovative solutions that suit the fast-growing Alibaba’s network and the needs of various business units across Alibaba.
Development and maintenance for current systems, working with network operation team troubleshoot complex network incidents.
Could work with business team closely to understand requirements, collect feedback and provide solutions and proposals, make network as service for users.
Qualifications
Familiar with Java /C++/Golang development, able to design big distribute system software with or without guidance. Familiar with Spring framework is a plus.
Working knowledge on database such as My-SQL,reddis and etc, with application development experience;
Working knowledge on network infrastructure and major protocols (e.g., SRTE/SRv6, BGP/anycast), familiar with SRTE or BGP/anycast is a big plus;
Experience with SDN, network traffic engineering, traffic management, traffic analysis, Internet ISP peering is much preferred;
Experience on big data analysis and knowledge of application development on big data platform;
Experience on optimization algorithms;
Experience on Linux kernel development especially network module.

The pay range for this position at commencement of employment is expected to be between $146,400/year and $240,000/year. However, base pay offered may vary depending on multiple individualized factors, including market location, job-related knowledge, skills, and experience.

If hired, employee will be in an “at-will position” and the Company reserves the right to modify base salary (as well as any other discretionary payment or compensation program) at any time, including for reasons related to individual performance, Company or individual department/team performance, and market factors.
